entry.def: To have a stranglehold on something means to have control over it and prevent it from being free or from developing.

example.ex: These companies are determined to keep a stranglehold on the banana industry...
example.tran: 这些公司决心要垄断香蕉业。

example.tran: 部队正在加强对该市的控制。
